{
  "title": "ISic000628. Epitaph of Abdalas",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: #JP</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"la\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>D(is) · m(anibus) · s(acrum) · <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Abdalas · Domi\n                    tiae · Domitiani\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Abdalas\">Abdalas</span> · <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Domi\n                    tiae · Domitiani\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Domi\n                    tiae\">Domi-<br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>tiae</span> · <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Domitiani\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Domitiani\">Domi<span class=\"tall\" title=\"tall character: t\">t</span>iani</span></span></span></span>  <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>magis<span class=\"tall\" title=\"tall character: t\">t</span>er · magnus <br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>ovium qui · bene · vix(it) <br id=\"al6-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>in officio · ann(os) · LXXX </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: #JP</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"la\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>D·M·S·<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Abdalas · Domi\n                    tiae · Domitiani\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Abdalas\">ABDALAS</span>·<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Domi\n                    tiae · Domitiani\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Domi\n                    tiae\">DOMI<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>TIAE</span>·<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Domitiani\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Domitiani\">DOMI<span class=\"tall\" title=\"tall character: t\">T</span>IANI</span></span></span></span><br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>MAGIS<span class=\"tall\" title=\"tall character: t\">T</span>ER·MAGNUS<br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>OVIUMQUI·BENE·VIX(IT)<br id=\"al6-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>INOFFICIO·ANN·LXXX</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text from photograph</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">Roger Wilson</p>  <p>Sacred to the spirits of the dead. Abdalas (slave) of Domitia (wife) of Domitian, head shepherd of the sheep, who lived well in his position, for eighty years.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>A parallel funerary inscription for Chius, magnus magister pecoris has now been found some 16km to the northwest (<a href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001693\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001693</a>)</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 1985.0483 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283</a></li><li> Salmeri 1984 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001608\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001608</a></li><li> Manganaro 1988 17 n.62 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427</a></li><li> Wilson 1990 215 n.102 fig.175 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001509\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001509</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
  "divs": [
    {
      "id": "editions",
      "html": "<div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: #JP</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"la\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>D(is) · m(anibus) · s(acrum) · <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Abdalas · Domi\n                    tiae · Domitiani\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Abdalas\">Abdalas</span> · <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Domi\n                    tiae · Domitiani\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Domi\n                    tiae\">Domi-<br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>tiae</span> · <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Domitiani\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Domitiani\">Domi<span class=\"tall\" title=\"tall character: t\">t</span>iani</span></span></span></span>  <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>magis<span class=\"tall\" title=\"tall character: t\">t</span>er · magnus <br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>ovium qui · bene · vix(it) <br id=\"al6-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>in officio · ann(os) · LXXX </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: #JP</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"la\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>D·M·S·<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Abdalas · Domi\n                    tiae · Domitiani\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type